data.description: ASK ABOUT 3.5% ASSUMABLE VA LOAN! Introducing this meticulously maintained home in Eagle Crest Ranch. Freshly painted, this 3-bedroom residence offers an additional office space. Step inside to discover new ceramic tile flooring in the main areas and plush carpeting in the bedrooms. Enjoy the privacy and shade of the large yard, complete with a built-in fireplace and towering trees. The front bedroom welcomes abundant natural light, while the split floor plan situates the primary bedroom at the rear of the home. Located just North of Oro Valley, this peaceful neighborhood offers a serene retreat with convenient access to shopping options and your Saddlebrooke friends. Don't miss your chance to call this delightful property home!
